akitaDAO.descr: the app ID of the Akita DAO

boxCount.descr: the number of boxes created during the poll

endTime.descr: the time the poll ends as a unix timestamp

gateID.descr: the gate id to be used for filtering who can interact with this poll

maxSelected.descr: the maximum number of selections in a multiple choice poll

optionCount.descr: the number of options in the poll

optionOne.descr: the options and vote counts of the poll

type.descr: The type of poll: SingleChoice, MultipleChoice, SingleChoiceImpact or MultipleChoiceImpact

version.descr: the current version of the contract

votesOne.descr: the number of votes for each option
